casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Warren Jay BRONSNICK.
No. D-2919.
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 8, 2016.
Warren Jay Bronsnick, of Short Hills, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
